** [[特島信天翁|特岛信天翁]] (''D. (exulans) dabbenena'')
** {{Le|北方皇家信天翁|Northern royal albatross}} (''D. (epomophora) sanfordi'')
** [[南方皇家信天翁|南方皇家信天翁]] (''D. epomophora'')
* {{Le|北太平洋信天翁属|North Pacific albatross}} (''Phoebastria'')
** {{Le|加岛信天翁|Waved albatross}} (''P. irrorata'')
** [[短尾信天翁|短尾信天翁]] (''P. albatrus'')
** [[黑脚信天翁|黑脚信天翁]] (''P. nigripes'')
** [[黑背信天翁|黑背信天翁]] (''P. immutabilis'')
* {{Le|小信天翁属|Mollymawk}} (''Thalassarche'')
** [[黑眉信天翁|黑眉信天翁]] (''T. melanophris'' )
** {{Le|坎岛信天翁|Campbell albatross}} (''T. (melanophris) impavida'')
** {{Le|羞怯信天翁|Shy albatross}} (''T. cauta'')
** {{Le|白顶信天翁|White-capped albatross}} (''T. (cauta) steadi'')
